'''扇肢亞目'''（學名：{{lang|la|Flabellifera}}）是一個[[甲殼亞門|甲殼亞門]][[軟甲綱|軟甲綱]][[等足目|等足目]]之下的一個[[棄用生物分類|棄用生物分類]]。這個亞目有超過3000物種，但後來證實若不是[[多系群|多系群]]的話，就是一個[[並系群|並系群]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.crustacea.net/crustace/www/flabelli.htm |title=Flabellifera |publisher=[[Australian_Museum|Australian Museum]] |author=J. K. Lowry |work=Crustacea: The Higher Taxa |language=en |date=1999-11-02 |accessdate=2011-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213163642/http://crustacea.net/crustace/www/flabelli.htm |archive-date=2010-12-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tolweb.org/notes/?note_id=4175 |title=Suborder Flabellifera |work=Guide to the Coastal Marine Isopods of California |author=Richard Brusca, Vania R. Coelho & Stefano Taiti |accessdate=January 28, 2009 |publisher=[[Tree_of_Life_Web_Project|Tree of Life Web Project]] |archive-date=2015-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417164108/http://tolweb.org/notes/?note_id=4175 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。所以現時其部分物種已分開了成為[[Sphaeromatidea|Sphaeromatidea]]，而餘下的物種跟原來的[[寄生亞目|寄生亞目]]合併，組成了新的[[縮頭水蝨亞目|縮頭水蝨亞目]]（Cymothoida）<ref>{{cite journal |title=Higher classification of the flabelliferan and related Isopoda based on a reappraisal of relationships |author=Angelika Brandt & Gary C. B. Poore |journal=[[Invertebrate_Systematics|Invertebrate Systematics]] |volume=17 |issue=6 |pages=893–923 |year=2003 |doi=10.1071/IS02032}}</ref><ref name="an">{{cite journal|journal=海洋科學|year=2005年|volume=第29卷|issue=第10期|url=http://159.226.158.205/hykx/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20051017&year_id=2005&quarter_id=10&falg=1|title=寄生亚目的系统研究概况以及我国寄生亚目的研究展望|author1=[[安建梅|安建梅]]|author2=[[于海燕|-{于}-海燕]]|author3=[[李新正|李新正]]|access-date=2015-04-20|archive-date=2015-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427144809/http://159.226.158.205/hykx/ch/reader/create_pdf.aspx?file_no=20051017&year_id=2005&quarter_id=10&falg=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

